<article id="post-751504" class="post-751504 digital-library type-digital-library status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry category-architecture-and-hardware category-society issue-march-2024 section-research content-type-has-video content-type-video-archive">

			
<header class="article-header article-header--dark">
	<div class="article-header__inner container">
		<div class="article-header__section"><a href="https://cacm.acm.org/section/research/">Research and Advances</a></div>
		<div class="article-header__topic-and-issue-section">
			<span class="article-header__topic">
			<a href="https://cacm.acm.org/category/architecture-and-hardware/">Architecture and Hardware</a>			</span>
			<span class="article-header__issue-section">
							</span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="article-header__title">The Internet of Batteryless Things</h1>
					<div class="article-header__subtitle"><p>Batteryless, energy-harvesting systems could reshape the Internet of Things into a more sustainable societal infrastructure.</p>
</div>
		
		<div class="article-header__meta">
			<div class="article-header__byline">
				By <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/saad-ahmed/" title="Posts by Saad Ahmed" class="author url fn" rel="author">Saad Ahmed</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/bashima-islam/" title="Posts by Bashima Islam" class="author url fn" rel="author">Bashima Islam</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/kasim-sinan-yildirim/" title="Posts by Kasim Sinan Yildirim" class="author url fn" rel="author">Kasim Sinan Yildirim</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/marco-zimmerling/" title="Posts by Marco Zimmerling" class="author url fn" rel="author">Marco Zimmerling</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/przemyslaw-pawelczak/" title="Posts by Przemysław Pawełczak" class="author url fn" rel="author">Przemysław Pawełczak</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/muhammad-hamad-alizai/" title="Posts by Muhammad Hamad Alizai" class="author url fn" rel="author">Muhammad Hamad Alizai</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/brandon-lucia/" title="Posts by Brandon Lucia" class="author url fn" rel="author">Brandon Lucia</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/luca-mottola/" title="Posts by Luca Mottola" class="author url fn" rel="author">Luca Mottola</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/jacob-sorber/" title="Posts by Jacob Sorber" class="author url fn" rel="author">Jacob Sorber</a>, and <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/josiah-hester/" title="Posts by Josiah Hester" class="author url fn" rel="author">Josiah Hester</a>			</div>
			<div class="article-header__posted-on">
				<span class="posted-on">Posted <time datetime="2024-02-21T13:55:52-05:00">Feb 21 2024</time></span>			</div>
		</div>

					<figure class="article-header__figure">
									<div class="video-wrapper">
						<iframe title="vimeo-player" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/905772290?h=0ab6348a69" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>					</div>
							</figure>
		
