</li>
<li class="ref">
<div id="B38" class="citation"><span class="label">38.</span> <span class="mixed-citation" data-jats-publication-type="book"><span class="person-group" data-jats-person-group-type="author"><span class="string-name"><span class="surname">van der Woude</span>, <span class="given-names">J.</span></span> and <span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Hicks</span>, <span class="given-names">M.</span></span>  </span><span class="article-title">Intermittent computation without hardware support or programmer intervention</span>. In <span class="source">Proceedings of OSDI (Savannah, GA, USA Nov. 2–4, 2016) </span>. <span class="publisher-name">ACM</span>, <span class="fpage">17</span>–<span class="lpage">32</span>; <a class="ext-link" href="https://www.usenix.org/system/files/conference/osdi16/osdi16-van-der-woude.pdf" data-jats-ext-link-type="uri">https://www.usenix.org/system/files/conference/osdi16/osdi16-van-der-woude.pdf</a>.</span></div>
